{
  "stem": "4686.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We kids were very happy, because we had the whole yard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and everybody was around us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it didn't bother us that we can't go out to the park to play.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had plenty of playing space at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think it-- it bothered us too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- it was more worry for our parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But our kids, it wasn't so much so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- that was, I think, May, end of May, that was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, the next thing what-- what I would remember is losing my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish council was doing the things what the government pushed them-- pushed them to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think the idea was that, if you don't do it, we will.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they organized the Jewish houses and organized the-- the people who did not live in-- in Jewish houses to move in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those who lived in Jewish houses to, instead of using two rooms, go into one, so that they can give the free houses to those who are bombed out, was the story.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I didn't know the people in the council.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one elderly gentlemen who told me that, now, you go to this street and tell these people to do this or that, or take this letter from here to there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 12 years old, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it-- it was a very scary thing to go in into people's homes and have a look how big it is, their-- their flat, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That they have two rooms, or three rooms, and how big is the room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that's how they picked up the data and organized it that, yes, it's a small room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We can only put two people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
